description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Warren Vache is a supremely accomplished, versatile and rare performer. He has been astounding audiences worldwide for decades with his superb cornet, trumpet and flugelhorn stylings. In this segment, Warren gives a basic lesson about the fingerings on the trumpet.
title: Warren Vache On Fingering Lessons for the Horn
